message.body: Hey!
What's up!?!
I have some really big news to tell you
What?!
ï¿¼Can you guess what it is?
OMG!!!!!!!! No way!!!! Congrats!!!!!

I take it you figured it out then haha. Thank you! I was totally played he sent a friend of ours to bitch about her boyfriend and say I wish he was like yours and was thinking about engagement and marriage just so she could report my reaction to him and then 2 days later he gave me a giant box filled with a never ending supply of smaller boxes
Aww! I'm so happy for you!! :D
It hasn't quite hit me yet I guess. I just keep thinking about how I used to never even want a boyfriend to being engaged
Aww my Kellee is all grown up!
I know. We grow up so fast haha
Lol true that
So what's new in your life?
Not much. Just got back from Vermont lol
Nothing as exciting as you!
Lol oh please this will be old news by tomorrow haha. What were you doing in vermont?
Planned it for my boyfriends birthday/Christmas gift.. He likes to snowboard.
That's sweet. Although I don't understand how anybody can like snowboarding lol but that's just me haha. I'm guessing it was a weekend trip?
Yep. We came home yesterday. I'm no fan of snowboarding either despite his attempts to make me like it

I have a solution to this problem. Mikey likes to snowboard and I am not a fan. You're boyfriend, who's name escapes me right now because I'm a jackass, likes to snowboard and you're not a fan so they meet they snowboard and we just sit around drinking "hot chocolate" all day
I like it! Lol his name is Charles
Okay I will remember that now lol. I thought it was a good plan
Lol me too

Random question, I mean really random, but I'm organizing all my school stuff because my folders are about to explode if I don't and I'm wondering if I should give all my tests one file and my assignments a different one or just put them in the same one, which would you do?
I would separate then
Them*

That's what I was thinking. Yeah I'm gonna do that and then I just need to set up another file for study guides. That was the problem I'm one file short and I didn't feel like stopping at the store after class tomorrow but I am
lol you got this
It's just driving me crazy. There's so many papers of clinicals and tests and everything else in the world
